title: Can You Eat Healthy on EBT?
itunes:title: Can You Eat Healthy on EBT?
description:
Today on the show we had Tiny and her daughter Zonnique call in where they spoke about connecting with millenials, getting ready for motherhood, Gen Z for new talk show "The Mix". Also, we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners knows how to eat healthy while on EBT, after Keke Palmer comments about eating healthy on EBT. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the Secretary of State of Kansas Kris Kobach for not being sure if he would still support Trump if he came out that he was racist.
